#: resources/animate.glade:78
msgid "Animated"
msgstr "Animé"

#: resources/animate.glade:85
msgid ""
"Hue shows the peak magnitude s(n); brightness follows the traveling wave |"
"cos(arg z + φ)|, floored so nulls stay visible.\n"
"\n"
"Animated: bright regions sweep along the structure as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"La teinte indique l'amplitude crête s(n) ; la luminosité suit l'onde "
"progressive |cos(arg z + φ)|, avec un plancher pour que les nœuds restent "
"visibles.\n"
"\n"
"Animé : les régions lumineuses balaient la structure à mesure que la phase "
"avance."

#: resources/animate.glade:86
msgid "Instantaneous"
msgstr "Instantané"

#: resources/animate.glade:96
msgid ""
"Diverging hue shows the instantaneous sign of the displayed quantity: cold "
"negative, hot positive; brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: regions swap poles as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"La teinte divergente indique le signe instantané de la grandeur affichée : "
"froid pour négatif, chaud pour positif ; la luminosité porte l'amplitude "
"s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animé : les régions changent de polarité à mesure que la phase avance."

#: resources/animate.glade:97
msgid "Polarity"
msgstr "Polarité"

#: resources/animate.glade:107
msgid ""
"Cyclic hue wheel shows the phase angle arg z + φ; brightness carries the "
"magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: the whole wheel rotates as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"La roue de teintes cyclique indique l'angle de phase arg z + φ ; la "
"luminosité porte l'amplitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animé : toute la roue tourne à mesure que la phase avance."

#: resources/animate.glade:108
msgid "Phase Hue"
msgstr "Teinte de phase"

#: resources/animate.glade:118
msgid ""
"Diverging hue shows the instantaneous charge sign; brightness carries the "
"current envelope s(|I|).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: one view of charge and current a quarter cycle apart."
msgstr ""
"La teinte divergente indique le signe instantané de la charge ; la "
"luminosité porte l'enveloppe de courant s(|I|).\n"
"\n"
"Animé : une vue unique de la charge et du courant décalés d'un quart de "
"cycle."

#: resources/animate.glade:119
msgid "Current + Charge"
msgstr "Courant + charge"

#: resources/animate.glade:136
msgid "Static"
msgstr "Statique"

#: resources/animate.glade:143
msgid ""
"Rainbow ramp of this frequency step's peak magnitude s(n) at full "
"brightness.\n"
"\n"
"Static: the phase-invariant baseline; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"Dégradé arc-en-ciel de l'amplitude crête s(n) de ce pas de fréquence, à "
"pleine luminosité.\n"
"\n"
"Statique : la base invariante en phase ; les couleurs restent fixes pendant "
"la lecture."

#: resources/animate.glade:144
msgid "Amplitude"
msgstr "Amplitude"

#: resources/animate.glade:154
msgid ""
"Hue ramps the per-region standing-wave ratio: cold traveling, hot standing; "
"brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Static: a phase-invariant read; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"La teinte suit le taux d'onde stationnaire par région : froid pour "
"progressive, chaud pour stationnaire ; la luminosité porte l'amplitude "
"s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Statique : une lecture invariante en phase ; les couleurs restent fixes "
"pendant la lecture."

#: resources/animate.glade:155
msgid "Standing/Traveling"
msgstr "Stationnaire/Progressive"

#: resources/animate.glade:165
msgid ""
"Hue ramps each segment's contribution to the selected far-field direction; "
"brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Static: a phase-invariant read; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"La teinte suit la contribution de chaque segment à la direction de champ "
"lointain sélectionnée ; la luminosité porte l'amplitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Statique : une lecture invariante en phase ; les couleurs restent fixes "
"pendant la lecture."

#: resources/animate.glade:166
msgid "Far-field Contribution"
msgstr "Contribution en champ lointain"

#: resources/animate.glade:180
msgid ""
"Power-law transfer n^γ of the normalized magnitude.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 1 is linear amplitude; γ = 0.5 expands weak regions; γ = 2 shows the "
"squared magnitude — |I|² is proportional to per-segment dissipated power "
"(and its radiated-power contribution via radiation resistance), |q|² to "
"stored electrostatic energy."
msgstr ""
"Transfert en loi de puissance n^γ de l'amplitude normalisée.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 1 correspond à une amplitude linéaire ; γ = 0,5 étend les régions "
"faibles ; γ = 2 affiche l'amplitude au carré — |I|² est proportionnel à la "
"puissance dissipée par segment (et à sa contribution à la puissance rayonnée "
"via la résistance de rayonnement), |q|² à l'énergie électrostatique stockée."

#: resources/animate.glade:181
msgid "Power"
msgstr "Puissance"

#: resources/animate.glade:191
msgid ""
"Logarithmic transfer over a user range R, the RF-standard 20·log₁₀ amplitude "
"decibels.\n"
"\n"
"R sets the visible dynamic range; detail below the floor 10^(−R/20) clips to "
"the bottom color."
msgstr ""
"Transfert logarithmique sur une plage utilisateur R, les décibels "
"d'amplitude 20·log₁₀ standard en RF.\n"
"\n"
"R définit la plage dynamique visible ; le détail sous le plancher 10^(−R/20) "
"est écrêté à la couleur la plus basse."

#: resources/animate.glade:192 resources/xnec2c.glade:11670
#: resources/xnec2c.glade:13045
msgid "dB"
msgstr "dB"

#: resources/animate.glade:202
msgid ""
"Inverse hyperbolic sine: linear below the knee k, logarithmic above.\n"
"\n"
"Keeps near-null currents visible while compressing strong peaks, like a lin-"
"log instrument scale."
msgstr ""
"Sinus hyperbolique inverse : linéaire en dessous du genou k, logarithmique "
"au-dessus.\n"
"\n"
"Maintient visibles les courants proches de zéro tout en compressant les pics "
"forts, comme une échelle d'instrument lin-log."

#: resources/animate.glade:203
msgid "Asinh"
msgstr "Asinh"

#: resources/animate.glade:213
msgid ""
"μ-law companding, the telephony-standard bounded log curve.\n"
"\n"
"Lifts weak detail without a hard floor; 48.16 dB compression is the classic "
"μ = 255."
msgstr ""
"Compression μ-law, la courbe logarithmique bornée standard de la "
"téléphonie.\n"
"\n"
"Rehausse les détails faibles sans plancher dur ; une compression de 48,16 dB "
"correspond au μ = 255 classique."

#: resources/animate.glade:214
msgid "μ-law"
msgstr "μ-law"

#: resources/animate.glade:224
msgid ""
"Reinhard rational compressor (1+k)·n/(n+k), the photographic HDR tone-map.\n"
"\n"
"Preserves midtones while rolling highlights off smoothly; k sets the knee."
msgstr ""
"Compresseur rationnel de Reinhard (1+k)·n/(n+k), le mappage tonal HDR "
"photographique.\n"
"\n"
"Préserve les tons moyens tout en atténuant en douceur les hautes lumières ; "
"k définit le genou."

#: resources/animate.glade:225
msgid "Reinhard"
msgstr "Reinhard"

#: resources/animate.glade:235
msgid ""
"Hyperbolic tangent soft limiter tanh(a·n)/tanh(a).\n"
"\n"
"Raises midrange contrast and saturates gently toward the peak, like "
"amplifier compression; a sets the steepness."
msgstr ""
"Limiteur doux en tangente hyperbolique tanh(a·n)/tanh(a).\n"
"\n"
"Augmente le contraste des tons moyens et sature en douceur vers le pic, "
"comme une compression d'amplificateur ; a définit la pente."

#: resources/animate.glade:236
msgid "Sigmoid"
msgstr "Sigmoïde"

#: resources/animate.glade:246
msgid ""
"Identity: every magnitude renders at full brightness.\n"
"\n"
"The color projection alone carries the information."
msgstr ""
"Identité : toute amplitude s'affiche à pleine luminosité.\n"
"\n"
"La projection de couleur seule porte l'information."

#: resources/animate.glade:247 resources/settings/cairo_settings.glade:56
msgid "None"
msgstr "Aucun"

