#: resources/animate.glade:491
msgid "Color projection:"
msgstr "Projection de couleur :"

#: resources/animate.glade:505
msgid ""
"Select which physical quantity drives the hue and how brightness follows the "
"excitation phase.\n"
"\n"
"Static projections (Amplitude, Standing/Traveling, Far-field Contribution) "
"read without animating.\n"
"\n"
"Hovering an entry previews it live."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner la grandeur physique qui pilote la teinte et la façon dont la "
"luminosité suit la phase d'excitation.\n"
"\n"
"Les projections statiques (Amplitude, Stationnaire/Progressive, Contribution "
"en champ lointain) se lisent sans animation.\n"
"\n"
"Survoler une entrée en affiche un aperçu en direct."

#: resources/animate.glade:532
msgid "Scale family:"
msgstr "Famille d'échelle :"

#: resources/animate.glade:546
msgid ""
"Select the magnitude-to-color transfer family.\n"
"\n"
"Adjust its slider until the contrast reveals the range your inspection "
"needs.\n"
"\n"
"Hovering an entry previews it live."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner la famille de transfert amplitude-couleur.\n"
"\n"
"Ajuster son curseur jusqu'à ce que le contraste révèle la plage nécessaire à "
"l'inspection.\n"
"\n"
"Survoler une entrée en affiche un aperçu en direct."

#: resources/animate.glade:585
msgid "Gamma:"
msgstr "Gamma :"

#: resources/animate.glade:602
msgid ""
"Gamma exponent of the power transfer.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 0.5 expands weak regions, γ = 1 is linear, γ = 2 is proportional to "
"dissipated power for currents."
msgstr ""
"Exposant gamma du transfert de puissance.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 0,5 étend les régions faibles, γ = 1 est linéaire, γ = 2 est "
"proportionnel à la puissance dissipée pour les courants."

#: resources/animate.glade:624
msgid "Range (dB):"
msgstr "Plage (dB) :"

#: resources/animate.glade:641
msgid ""
"Dynamic range R below the step peak mapped onto the color strip.\n"
"\n"
"The floor is 10^(−R/20) of the peak."
msgstr ""
"Plage dynamique R sous le pic du pas mappée sur la bande de couleur.\n"
"\n"
"Le plancher est 10^(−R/20) du pic."

#: resources/animate.glade:663
msgid "Softening:"
msgstr "Adoucissement :"

#: resources/animate.glade:680
msgid "Softening knee k: linear below k, logarithmic above."
msgstr ""
"Genou d'adoucissement k : linéaire en dessous de k, logarithmique au-dessus."

#: resources/animate.glade:702
msgid "Compression (dB):"
msgstr "Compression (dB) :"

#: resources/animate.glade:719
msgid "Compression strength in dB; higher values lift weak detail."
msgstr ""
"Force de compression en dB ; des valeurs plus élevées rehaussent les détails "
